Please install sdcc to build stm8s under ubuntu
Ubuntu 14.10
        sudo apt-get install sdcc
Ubuntu 14.04
        sudo add-apt-repository ppa:laczik/ppa
        sudo apt-get update
        sudo apt-get remove sdcc sdcc-libraries
        sudo apt-get install sdcc

Tool to flash
git clone https://github.com/vdudouyt/stm8flash.git
cd stm8flash
make
sudo make install

Please refer link for more infor
http://www.cnx-software.com/2015/04/13/how-to-program-stm8s-1-board-in-linux/
